title: Zeit Of The Talkyries 11/20: Deadpool 3, Animaniacs, Rick Scott, NBA, Nielsen Ratings
itunes:title: Zeit Of The Talkyries 11/20: Deadpool 3, Animaniacs, Rick Scott, NBA, Nielsen Ratings
description:
On this edition of Zeit Of The Talkyries Jack and DJ Danl discuss Deadpool 3 being in the works, the Animaniacs being back on Hulu, Rick Scott has contracted COVID, the Raptors are playing in Tampa Bay and Klay Thompson is out for the entire season with an Achilles tear, and how Netflix dominates the Nielsen ratings.
